                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.3396/2–347: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Stuart</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1947-02-05T15:00:00-05:00"
                            >February 5, 1947—3 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>141. I fully concur in views expressed your 193 Feb 3, 7 p.m. and am taking up
                    matter with Secretary Forrestal.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Marshall</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
